name: Ayanami (Azur Lane)
description:
Use to 1 ~ 0.8

You can create a total of 11 outfits.

She can change into different outfits and hairstyles by filling out the prompts!

The keywords are '(costume), silver_hair'.

If her outfit is not generating well, write additional prompts.

1.Normal

ayanami, silver hair,

2.Wedding

kimono, silver_ hair, off_shoulder, hair_ornament, navel,

3.Rock 'n' Demon

4.Grade A Sailor Uniform

5.Pulse of the New Year

6.Nightfall Raiment

dress, silver hair, frills,

7.Lunar Demon

8.Low-Key Idol @Confused

9.NicoNico

sleepwear, silver hair, white shirt,

10.Witch in Ambush

11.Dynamic Kick
